nce ([[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|SNEP]])<ref name=\"heid\u00e9\">{{cite book|first=Heid\u00e9|last=Gustave|title=Le Singles Platine de la Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique (1992)|trans-title=Singles certified Platinum by the Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique in 1992|edition=9|location=Paris, France|publisher=Decoverts|language=fr}} Translated quote: 'Tears in Heaven' spent 34 weeks on the national french singles chart and peaked at number two, making it Eric Clapton's most popular single in France. It was requested to be certified Platinum on chart week 28 by Reprise (Warner) Records.</ref>\n|2\n|-\n{{singlechart|Germany|42|artist=Clapton, Eric|refname=ger|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 12, 2015}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Iceland ([[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]])<ref>{{cite web |url=http://timarit.is/view_page_init.jsp?issId=193979&pageId=2596605&lang=en&q=Clapton|title=Vins\u00e6idaiisti \u00edsiands|publisher=Dagbla\u00f0i\u00f0 V\u00edsir|date=1992-03-27|accessdate=August 2, 2016}}</ref>\n|1\n|-\n{{singlechart|Ireland2|1|song=Tears in Heaven|refname=irl|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 12, 2015}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Italy ([[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]])\n|5\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Italy ([[Musica e dischi]])<ref name=\"md\">{{cite web|url=http://musicaedischi.it/web/classifiche_archivio.php|title=M&D: Classifiche|trans-title=M&D: Charts|language=it|publisher=Musica e dischi|id=Search for Eric Clapton as the artist, then select the song \"Tears in Heaven\" to see the highest chart position.|location=Italy|url-access=registration |accessdate=November 12, 2015}}</ref>\n|4\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Japan ([[Oricon|''Oricon'' Hot 100 Singles]])<ref name=\"japan100\">{{cite web|url=http://www.j-wave.co.jp/original/tokiohot100/cgi-bin/top100.cgi|title=Hot 100 Chart 1992-02-04|language=ja|publisher=J-Wave Japan|work=Oricon Style|accessdate=November 12, 2015}}</ref>\n|2\n|-